   "source": [
    "from src.preprocess import resolve_language, preprocess_text\n",
    "from src.evaluate import run_sbert_pipeline\n",
    "\n",
    "sample_article = \"\"\"\n",
    "Artificial intelligence is transforming industries across the globe at an unprecedented pace.\n",
    "Recent advances in natural language processing allow computers to understand and summarize complex documents in seconds.\n",
    "Extractive summarization techniques select the most informative sentences directly from the source text.\n",
    "By leveraging Sentence-BERT embeddings, machines can capture deep semantic relationships between sentences.\n",
    "K-Means clustering helps group similar concepts together, ensuring the final summary covers diverse perspectives.\n",
    "Post-filtering techniques further eliminate redundant information, producing concise and highly relevant summaries for users.\n",
    "This hybrid pipeline represents a robust approach for modern automated text summarization systems.\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
